Date: 0/0/1988
Source: Dictionary of Kiwi Slang, A
Author: McGILL
Vol / Page: 49
Edition:
Quote: <i>give someone curry</i> to abuse or razz vigorously, aften in sport; from the heat associated with curry; eg `That useless Aussie bowler, did we give him some curry!' NZA.
